Folder to contain the Debian package control scripts used to create 
the *deb packages.

Instruction
- Update debian/changelog with adequate information
- Do a testrun by moving to main source dir and execute

  ./bldscripts/mkdebpkg -v<version> -r<release> -n

- When everything works push up a relase with

  ./bldscripts/mkdebpkg -v<version> -r<release> -u


NOTE: Needs PGP keys in ~/.gnupg


